<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_New_Space_Opera" title="The New Space Opera">The New Space Opera</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Gardner_Dozois" title="Gardner Dozois">Gardner Dozois</a> and <a href="/wiki/Jonathan_Strahan" title="Jonathan Strahan">Jonathan Strahan</a> (2007)</li>
